  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the effect of eleclazine (GS-6615) on exercise capacity, quality of
      life, and safety and tolerability of eleclazine in participants with symptomatic
      hypertrophic cardiomyopathy (HCM).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
